summary: An ordinance transferring the sum of Eight Hundred Dollars ($800.00) heretofore appropriated by Ordinance No. 23710, to complete the grading of 12th Avenue West from the general fund to the special fund for Local Improvement District No. 2204, created by Ordinance No. 22115, for the improvement of 12th Avenue West, by constructing concrete sidewalks etc thereon.
